Package com.onlinepayments.sdk.client.android.asynctask

Interface PaymentProductNetworkAsyncTask.PaymentProductNetworkListener

Enclosing class:
PaymentProductNetworkAsyncTask
@Deprecated public static interface PaymentProductNetworkAsyncTask.PaymentProductNetworkListener
Deprecated.
Use PaymentProductNetworkResponseListener instead.
Callback Interface that is invoked when the Payment Product Network request completes. In case of an error and/or exception, the onPaymentProductNetworkError(ErrorResponse) callback will be invoked. On success the onPaymentProductNetworkCallComplete(PaymentProductNetworkResponse) callback will be invoked.
